  - Host resolution/connectivity unavailable on this machine at runtime.
- Implemented fast-fail behavior (no long indefinite waiting):
  - backend returns 503 quickly when DB unreachable.
  - frontend request timeout + clearer login timeout message.
- Checked Docker availability:
  - Docker CLI present.
  - Docker Desktop daemon was not running (engine pipe unavailable), so local Mongo container could not be started from CLI yet.


